    "crafted": {
      "type": "media-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "media": {
          "type": "_media-without-appearance",
          "static": true,
          "settings": {
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/crafted-germany-bread.png",
            "image_position": "cover"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "_content-without-appearance",
          "static": true,
          "settings": {
            "horizontal_alignment_flex_direction_column": "flex-start",
            "vertical_alignment_flex_direction_column": "center",
            "gap": 20
          },
          "blocks": {
            "heading": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2>crafted in germany. enjoyed fresh.</h2>",
                "type_preset": "h2",
                "alignment": "left",
                "font": "var(--font-heading--family)"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "body": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>At Bäckeli, we work with specialized German bakeries that have perfected their craft over generations.</p><p>Using traditional recipes and professional baking methods, our breads, rolls, and pastries are crafted in Germany and enjoyed fresh by guests and customers around the world.</p><p>The result is the unmistakable aroma, crisp crust, and authentic taste that have made German baking famous worldwide.</p>",
                "type_preset": "rte",
                "alignment": "left",
                "max_width": "narrow"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            }
          },
          "block_order": ["heading", "body"]
        }
      },
      "name": "t:names.media_with_text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "left",
        "media_width": "medium",
        "media_height": "60svh",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "extend_media": true,
        "background_color": "#FCFCFC",
        "padding-block-start": 0,
        "padding-block-end": 0
      }
    },
